(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/bedrock/latest/APIReference/API_runtime_ConverseStream.html).

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Content => ArrayRef[L<Paws::BedrockRuntime::ContentBlock>]

The message content. Note the following restrictions:

=over

=item *

You can include up to 20 images. Each image's size, height, and width
must be no more than 3.75 MB, 8000 px, and 8000 px, respectively.

=item *

You can include up to five documents. Each document's size must be no
more than 4.5 MB.

=item *

If you include a C<ContentBlock> with a C<document> field in the array,
you must also include a C<ContentBlock> with a C<text> field.

=item *

You can only include images and documents if the C<role> is C<user>.

=back



=head2 B<REQUIRED> Role => Str

The role that the message plays in the message.



